	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Apr 26th 2:55 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>well i will just have to disagree with you on the soloing, some people do not get money from higher level friends, they have to earn it.  i go out and kill and loot everything that i see with a weapon, even if it green. that is how i get my money, i am lvl 13 and just barely have all leather some chain and a luck loot bronze bracer from unrest, what you do not understand is that not everyone is so well off i used a bronze mace until i was lvl 16! I am sure it is easy to solo when you have a weapon that can compete with a warrior but face it most people cannot! you people really must go and make a new char, and get no help from anyone go and see how hard it is to buy spells and good items when you cant just pull the money out your arse! i m sorry but on my non-twink char, i would kill for 50pp that is prolly chunmpchange for all you twinks! and I would give up a few level for an ssb. so for real try it make someone without help and see if you are good enough.<br><br>Dididain<br>29 cleric of tunare<br>one of the last untwinked clerics *sigh*<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
